name: Master of None
overview: 30-year-old New York actor Dev takes on such pillars of maturity as the first big job, a serious relationship, and busting sex offenders on the subway.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Chronicling the relationship of Denise and her partner Alicia, Season three is a modern love story that intimately illustrates the ups and downs of marriage, struggles with fertility, and personal growth both together and apart. Fleeting romantic highs meet crushing personal losses while existential questions of love and living are raised.

tagline: This is Dev. He has a lot of questions.

episodes.name: Plan B
episodes.overview: A condom mishap and a kid's birthday party prompt Dev to consider the reality of having children.

episodes.name: Parents
episodes.overview: First-generationers Dev and Brian try to show their appreciation for their immigrant parents at a joint family dinner.

episodes.name: Hot Ticket
episodes.overview: Dev's plan to score a date with a pretty waitress by inviting her to a concert doesn't have quite the result he wanted.

episodes.name: Indians on TV
episodes.overview: Dev has a series of eye-opening experiences after he encounters some casual racism in TV auditions.

episodes.name: The Other Man
episodes.overview: Dev has the chance to hook up with a woman he meets at a party, but the opportunity comes with a few complications.

episodes.name: Nashville
episodes.overview: For his first official date with Rachel, Dev decides to go big and take her to Nashville for the weekend.

episodes.name: Ladies and Gentlemen
episodes.overview: Rachel and Denise school Dev and Arnold about the difficulties of being a woman in a world of creepy dudes. Dev is inspired to embrace feminism.

episodes.name: Old People
episodes.overview: An unexpected death inspires Dev and Rachel to visit Rachel's grandmother, while Arnold contends with a strange inheritance.

episodes.name: Mornings
episodes.overview: Dev and Rachel discover that living together isn't always going to be a series of happy mornings free from conflict and dirty clothes on the floor.

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: After attending a wedding and a movie premiere, Dev and Rachel have to face up to all kinds of issues between them.

episodes.name: The Thief
episodes.overview: While studying pasta making in Italy, Dev makes a serendipitous connection on his birthday, only to have his plans upended by a thief.

episodes.name: Le Nozze
episodes.overview: Arnold stops by on his way to a wedding to explore Modena with his Little Bud. But he hasn't told Dev the whole truth about his trip.

episodes.name: Religion
episodes.overview: Back in New York, a visit from observant Muslim relatives puts Dev in a tricky position. He introduces his cousin to a forbidden pleasure: pork.

episodes.name: First Date
episodes.overview: Sucked into a popular dating app, Dev winds up on a string of awkward, fun and disorienting dates with very different women.

episodes.name: The Dinner Party
episodes.overview: After welcoming the Jabbawockeez to his show, Dev struggles to find the right date to take to a dinner party thrown by his celebrity chef boss.

episodes.name: New York, I Love You
episodes.overview: As Dev and friends head to a theater to see the hit movie "Death Castle," the lives of several ordinary New Yorkers intersect in subtle ways.

episodes.name: Door #3
episodes.overview: A sweet job offer forces Dev to take stock of his priorities. Brian helps his dad with a romantic dilemma. A cupcake competition judge gets cold feet.

episodes.name: Thanksgiving
episodes.overview: Over a series of Thanksgivings from the '90s to the present, Denise settles into her sexuality and faces the challenge of coming out to her family.

episodes.name: Amarsi Un Po
episodes.overview: When Francesca returns to New York for a month, Dev plays tour guide and finds himself caught in a whirlwind of confusing emotions.

episodes.name: Buona Notte
episodes.overview: Just as Dev's personal life reaches a tipping point, disturbing revelations throw his professional life into turmoil, too.

episodes.name: Moments in Love, Chapter 1
episodes.overview: Now a bestselling author, Denise leads a quiet life with her wife, Alicia, in upstate New York. But dinner with another couple leads to bigger questions.

episodes.name: Moments in Love, Chapter 2
episodes.overview: As the mood in the house grows more strained, Alicia leaves town for an antique fair.

episodes.name: Moments in Love, Chapter 3
episodes.overview: Facing a wave of major changes in her life, Denise wrestles with feelings of guilt and failure.

episodes.name: Moments in Love, Chapter 4
episodes.overview: Alicia turns to a fertility clinic for help and soon finds herself on a physical, financial and emotional odyssey.

episodes.name: Moments in Love, Chapter 5
episodes.overview: A trip upstate leads to reflections on the past and present.
